event CreateTransaction(uint256 id, bytes[] data, uint256 deadline, uint8 status)
event ExecuteTransaction(uint256 id, bytes[] data, address executor)
event ExecuteUniswapTransaction(uint256 id, address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, address toAddress)
function assetBaseCurrencyPrice(address asset, uint256 amount) view returns (uint256)
function assetEthPrice(address asset, uint256 amount) view returns (uint256)

function decodeUniswapDataAfterSwap(address to, bytes _data, uint256 amount, bytes swapResult) view returns (address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, bool estimatedIn, bool estimatedOut)

function decodeUniswapDataBeforeSwap(address to, bytes _data, uint256 amount) view returns (address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOut, bool estimatedIn, bool estimatedOut)
function ethAssetPrice(address asset, uint256 ethAmount) view returns (uint256)
function exactInput(tuple(bytes path, address recipient, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOutMinimum) params) pure returns (address, address, uint256, uint256, bool, bool)

function exactInputSingle(tuple(address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint24 fee, address recipient, uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOutMinimum, uint160 sqrtPriceLimitX96) params) pure returns (address, address, uint256, uint256, bool, bool)
function exactOutput(tuple(bytes path, address recipient, uint256 amountOut, uint256 amountInMaximum) params) pure returns (address, address, uint256, uint256, bool, bool)

function exactOutputSingle(tuple(address tokenIn, address tokenOut, uint24 fee, address recipient, uint256 amountOut, uint256 amountInMaximum, uint160 sqrtPriceLimitX96) params) pure returns (address, address, uint256, uint256, bool, bool)

function initialize(tuple(address dao, address executor, uint256 executorTeamId, address[] approvers, uint256 approverTeamId, uint256 minApproval, string text, string transactionType, uint256 startTime, uint256 endTime, bool allowUnlimitedUsageCount, uint256 usageCount, address team) params, address[] _fromTokens, bool _allowAllToTokens, address[] _toTokens, bool _allowAnyAmount, uint256 _totalAmount, uint8 _amountPercentage, address _baseCurrency)
function swapExactTokensForTokens(uint256 amountIn, uint256 amountOutMin, address[] path, address) pure returns (address, address, uint256, uint256, bool, bool)
function swapTokensForExactTokens(uint256 amountOut, uint256 amountInMax, address[] path, address) pure returns (address, address, uint256, uint256, bool, bool)
function transactions(uint256) view returns (uint256 id, uint8 status, uint256 deadline, uint256 approvedCount, bool isExist)
function upgradeToAndCall(address newImplementation, bytes data) payable
